    <div class="container">
        <div class="tips-grid">
            
            <div class="tip-card">
                <div class="tip-image-container">
                    <img src="https://i.pinimg.com/736x/66/e5/5d/66e55d0d710003f83714b98ae93d8bcd.jpg" alt="Travel Tips for Japan" class="tip-image">
                </div>
                <div class="tip-content">
                    <h2 class="tip-country-name">Japan</h2>
                    <p class="tip-text">Do carry cash. While many places accept cards, smaller shops and restaurants, especially in rural areas, are often cash-only. Don't tip; it's not customary and can even be considered rude.</p>
                    <button class="tip-btn">Learn More!</button>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="tip-card">
                <div class="tip-image-container">
                    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1526481280693-3bfa7568e0f3?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&auto=format&fit=crop&w=600&q=80" alt="Travel Tips for South Korea" class="tip-image">
                </div>
                <div class="tip-content">
                    <h2 class="tip-country-name">South Korea</h2>
                    <p class="tip-text">Do take off your shoes when entering homes, temples, and some restaurants. Don't be afraid to try street food, but be aware that it's often spicy!</p>
                    <button class="tip-btn">Learn More!</button>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="tip-card">
                <div class="tip-image-container">
                    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1488747279002-c8523379faaa?fm=jpg&q=60&w=3000&ixlib=rb-4.1.0&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxzZWFyY2h8OHx8dW5pdGVkJTIwa2luZ2RvbXxlbnwwfHwwfHx8MA%3D%3D" alt="Travel Tips for United Kingdom" class="tip-image">
                </div>
                <div class="tip-content">
                    <h2 class="tip-country-name">United Kingdom</h2>
                    <p class="tip-text">Do bring a reusable water bottle; public fountains are common. Don't stand on the left side of escalators in the London Underground; it's for people walking up.</p>
                    <button class="tip-btn">Learn More!</button>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="tip-card">
                <div class="tip-image-container">
                    <img src="https://wallpapers.com/images/hd/4k-landscape-lake-lungern-switzerland-e1yv0sqq5seojy9n.jpg" alt="Travel Tips for Switzerland" class="tip-image">
                </div>
                <div class="tip-content">
                    <h2 class="tip-country-name">Switzerland</h2>
                    <p class="tip-text">Do invest in a Swiss Travel Pass if you plan on using public transport extensively. Don't be late; punctuality is highly valued and expected for meetings and appointments.</p>
                    <button class="tip-btn">Learn More!</button>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="tip-card">
                <div class="tip-image-container">
                    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1503614472-8c93d56e92ce?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&auto=format&fit=crop&w=600&q=80" alt="Travel Tips for Canada" class="tip-image">
                </div>
                <div class="tip-content">
                    <h2 class="tip-country-name">Canada</h2>
                    <p class="tip-text">Do embrace the outdoors, but be prepared for varying weather. Don't forget to pack layers. Don't forget to tip servers and bartenders, as it's a significant part of their income.</p>
                    <button class="tip-btn">Learn More!</button>
                </div>
            </div>
            
